snippet.title: Little Chinese Final Edition [SHARP X68000] (Long Play)
snippet.description:
Little Chinese Final Edition (リトルチャイニーズ) on the Sharp X68000. Long play, clear all though this game is fairly simple. This was the 2nd time I played it. Great little Street Fighter 2 clone only featuring Chun Li and variations.


#LittleChinese #SharpX68000 #StreetFighter2
